orning runner in Central Park, she launched her own athleisure brand three years ago.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sporting attire\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a keen morning runner\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1913}, {\"ngram\": \"Central Park\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"her own athleisure brand\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressing some 150 Irish Olympians has been a major challenge for the designer who pitched the idea to the Olympic Federation of Ireland in September 2021 and whose uniforms reflect a balance between tradition and contemporary trends.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"score\": 0.683748757835476, \"rank\": 0.4605823403929589, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major challenge\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the designer\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Federation\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"whose uniforms\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"a balance\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"contemporary trends\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud to represent and interpret Ireland's identity on a global stage\\\", she said.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999637894483017, \"rank\": 3.621181260317651e-0